          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Z707810P-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707810P-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z707810P-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-1" n="1">Unto Prelatick Order you'd ascend</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-2" n="2">Come on, J'll shew you how to do't, My Friend,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-3" n="3">Do not in Study waste the precious Day,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-4" n="4">To <hi rend="large-writing">necessary</hi> Knowledge short's the Way,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-5" n="5">Turn over a few Books, and learn to prate;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-6" n="6">Leave others solidly Things to debate:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-7" n="7">Load not with serious Piety your Breast;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-8" n="8">Alas! at <hi rend="large-writing">Court</hi> 'tis nothing but a Jest;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-9" n="9">Yet let a feigned Gravity take place,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-10" n="10">And Complaisance still dwell upon your face,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-11" n="11">Within your parish never should you stay, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-12" n="12">Nor to your People Preach or with them Pray,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-13" n="13">Your <hi rend="large-writing">Constant Business</hi> lyes another way.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-14" n="14">To please great Men must your chief Study be,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-15" n="15">And win the Ladies too with────── Pleasantry.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-16" n="16">Follow these Rules with Care, if you be wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z707810P-line-17" n="17">Experience shews 'tis the best way to rise.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
